RHEL 7  : https://wiki.opencrowbar.org/display/DCT/Automated+RH+OSP+installation+-+RHEL7


Some of the not so obvious settings : 

xxxx.properties - storage node : osd_disks : 
  This relates to OSD disks to create on each storage node ( see Ceph integration document.
  
settings.ini : 
  vip_private_network_range_start=xxxxxxx
  vip_public_network_range_start=xxxxxxx
  VIP range start on the private/public network assigned to HA services
